# Per-host Ansible vars holding this machine's REAL IPs/subnets — must never reach
# the public repo. The committed template is host_vars/*.yml.example.
# (This .gitignore is force-added: the global excludesfile normally ignores
#  .gitignore itself — see CLAUDE.md — but here it deliberately protects a secret-ish
#  file across clones, so it is tracked.)
bootstrap/host_vars/*.yml
!bootstrap/host_vars/*.yml.example
